gin blocks during WorldUpdateBegin, when gazebo closes it will do so without writing to the log. This can be reproduced using the blocking plugin on <a href=\"#!/osrf/gazebo/issues/2224/gazebo-splashscreen-up-forever-if-plugin\" rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"Gazebo Splashscreen up forever if plugin blocks during WorldUpdateBegin\" class=\"ap-connect-link\">#2224</a>.</p>\n<p>A workaround is to make the plugin stop blocking prior to gazebo shutting down.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2017-03-22T20:04:51.548853+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2017-03-22T20:10:02.306981+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 2236}